Enum RequestStatus

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<RequestStatus>
public enum RequestStatus
extends Enum<RequestStatus>

Describe the possible status values form a Request - CANCELED/GRANTED/REJECTED status should be on position n-2/n-1/n - ideal situation = one status for each granter involved in the approval strategy

Author:
fmacicasan
